tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_transactions (
  user_id INT,
  transaction_id INT,
  transaction_type VARCHAR,
  transaction_amount DECIMAL(10,2),
  transaction_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE InvestmentReports (
    user_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    total_investment DECIMAL,
    regulatory_compliance_status BOOLEAN,
    report_comments TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_transactions (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  transaction_id INT,
  transaction_date DATE,
  transaction_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE investment_reports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  report_date DATE,
  investment_value DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE regulatory_compliance (
  regulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  report_id INT,
  compliance_status VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    trans_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    trans_date DATE,
    trans_amount DECIMAL,
    trans_description TEXT
);
